1754	  \uses{def:gr_transition_pre}
1755	  The \emph{restricted-diagonal comorphism} on the patch \(U^I \times_{\mathbb{Z}}
1756	  U^J\) is the \(\mathbb{Z}\)-algebra homomorphism
1757	  \[
1758	    \delta_{I,J} : \mathbb{Z}[X^I] \otimes_{\mathbb{Z}} \mathbb{Z}[X^J]
1759	    \longrightarrow R^I_J,
1760	    \qquad
1761	    X^I \otimes 1 \mapsto X^I, \quad
1762	    1 \otimes X^J \mapsto (X^I_J)^{-1} X^I,
1763	  \]
1764	  whose surjectivity is the content of separatedness; this is the \(\delta_{I,J}\)
1765	  of \cref{lem:gr_separated}.
