2058	
2059	% SOURCE QUOTE PROOF: "The intersection of the diagonal of $\grass(r,d)$ with
2060	% $U^I\times U^J$ can be seen to be the closed subscheme
2061	% $\Delta_{I,J}\subset U^I\times U^J$ defined by entries of the matrix formula
